## Third-Party Libraries

This project uses the following third-party libraries:

### I2Cdevlib-MPU6050
- Author: Jeff Rowberg
- License: MIT License
- Repository: https://github.com/jrowberg/i2cdevlib
- Used for: MPU6050 IMU interface and control

### PID Library
- Author: Brett Beauregard
- License: MIT License  
- Repository: https://github.com/br3ttb/Arduino-PID-Library
- Used for: PID control algorithms for motion control

### Arduino Core Libraries
- Wire Library (I2C communication)
- Servo Library (Servo motor control)
- Standard Arduino libraries are provided under various open-source licenses

## Hardware Components

This software is designed to work with common, commercially available hardware:
- Arduino Uno/Nano/Pro Mini (Atmel ATmega328P)
- MPU6050 6-axis IMU
- HC-SR04 Ultrasonic Distance Sensor
- TB6612FNG Motor Driver
- Standard RC Servo Motors
- DC Gear Motors

No proprietary hardware is required.